    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next big adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or those fun weekend getaways. It runs great and looks even better in person. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home where it'll be appreciated as much as I\u2019ve enjoyed it. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
