    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit boasts individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system refresh to ensure precise variable valve timing. The chassis remains taut with upgraded poly-bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining the legendary 50/50 weight distribution and sharp turn-in. While the exterior shows honest signs of spirited use, the drivetrain is dialed in for peak performance, offering a visceral, analog connection to the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
