      "description": "This vehicle offers a refined driving experience, blending sophisticated engineering with a well-preserved aesthetic. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though a close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the premium leather upholstery shows only light creasing on the driver's side bolster, and the dashboard remains free of any sun damage or cracks. All interior technology, including the navigation system and heated seats, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, with a complete service history documenting regular oil changes and a recent brake pad replacement. It handles with precision and delivers smooth, consistent power. This is an ideal choice for a buyer looking for a dependable, high-end vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for many more miles.",
