      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This unit remains mechanically robust, featuring a recently serviced VANOS system and documented subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp engagement, transferring power through a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings, ensuring precise turn-in and excellent lateral stability. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the valvetrain synchronization and chassis integrity are exceptional. A visceral, high-revving machine for the discerning pilot.",
